        <a href="getting-started/basic-populating-data">Start Learning <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
    </div>

    <div class="home-card">
        <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i> Line Charts</h3>
        <p>Explore line, spline, and step line charts for displaying trends and continuous data.</p>
        <a href="chart-types/line-charts">View Examples <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
    </div>

    <div class="home-card">
        <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-column"></i> Bar & Column Charts</h3>
        <p>Create vertical columns and horizontal bars to compare values across categories.</p>
        <a href="chart-types/bar-column-charts">View Examples <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
    </div>

    <div class="home-card">
        <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pie"></i> Pie Charts</h3>
